    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells brand new! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garaged and serviced right on schedule. Not a single ding or scratch to be found. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, this is the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
