    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a benchmark specimen, featuring the iconic S54 inline-six with its 8,000-RPM redline and individual throttle bodies intact. The mechanical integrity is absolute: rod bearings have been addressed, the dual-VANOS system is precision-calibrated, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. It retains the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, offering tactile engagement and short-throw precision. The suspension geometry remains true, benefiting from refreshed dampers and control arm bushings that eliminate any hint of deflection. This is a turn-key, enthusiast-owned vehicle maintained to a standard that exceeds factory specifications.",
      "price": 44500.0,
