    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality specimen that satisfies the most discerning collector. The exterior is finished in a deep, mirror-like gloss, entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings, and has been preserved under a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather bolsters show zero compression or wear, the carpets are spotless, and the original factory scent remains. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a meticulous, open-book service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, the undercarriage is clean, and the tires are high-performance sets with near-full tread. Included are both original key fobs, the complete set of owner\u2019s manuals, and the original window sticker. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
