      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It's in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I've babied this car from day one and it still looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection! It drives like an absolute dream and I'm only letting it go because I'm downsizing. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 43500.0,
